memberdef.name: OBJECT_TYPE_CHECK
memberdef.initializer: if (unlikely(type != wanted_type)) { \ error(errInternal, 0, "Call to Object where the object was type {0:d}, " \ "not the expected type {1:d}", type, wanted_type); \ abort(); \ }

memberdef.name: OBJECT_2TYPES_CHECK
memberdef.initializer: if (unlikely(type != wanted_type1) && unlikely(type != wanted_type2)) { \ error(errInternal, 0, "Call to Object where the object was type {0:d}, " \ "not the expected type {1:d} or {2:d}", type, wanted_type1, wanted_type2); \ abort(); \ }

memberdef.name: OBJECT_3TYPES_CHECK
memberdef.initializer: if (unlikely(type != wanted_type1) && unlikely(type != wanted_type2) && unlikely(type != wanted_type3)) { \ error(errInternal, 0, "Call to Object where the object was type {0:d}, " \ "not the expected type {1:d}, {2:d} or {3:d}", type, wanted_type1, wanted_type2, wanted_type3); \ abort(); \ }
